  "Aperol|Clam Chowder": "Aperol's crisp bitter-orange-aperitivo edge overpowers the chowder's creamy clam-and-potato base -- the plate deserves Keenan Chardonnay, Far Niente Chardonnay, or Jean-Pierre Grossot Chablis, not a bitter aperitivo. Avoid; the alts above are the call. Aperol belongs on the steak course.",
