  "Aperol|Escargot": "Aperol's crisp bitter-orange-aperitivo edge overpowers the escargot's garlic-herb-butter savory weight -- the plate deserves Green Chartreuse, Mata Hari Absinthe, or Daniel Chotard Sancerre Rouge, not a bitter aperitivo. Avoid; reach for any of those instead. Save the Aperol for the steak course.",
  "Aperol|Faroe Island Salmon": "Aperol's crisp bitter-orange-aperitivo edge overpowers the salmon's rich oily flesh -- the plate deserves Cristom Mt Jefferson Cuvée, Lingua Franca Avni Pinot Noir, or Elk Cove Five Mountain, not a bitter aperitivo. Avoid; pick from the alternatives. Save the Aperol for the steak course.",
