  "Aperol|Grilled Caesar": "Aperol with the grilled Caesar — soft aperitivo against charred romaine and anchovy. Excellent; Aperol's orange-rhubarb lifts the Caesar at a softer register than Campari — spritz-friendly, brunch-adjacent match.",
