  "Aperol|Honey Roasted Carrots": "Aperol's crisp bitter-orange-aperitivo edge overpowers the honey carrots' honey-glazed carrot sweetness -- the plate deserves Schloss Vollrads Riesling, Lingua Franca Avni Pinot Noir, or Cristom Mt Jefferson Cuvée, not a bitter aperitivo. Avoid; pick from the alternatives. Aperol belongs on the steak course.",
