  "Austin Hope Cabernet Sauvignon|Bone Marrow": "Bone Marrow: this rich, umami-forward starter's bold fat and concentrated savory depth meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's tannin scrubs the starter's fat while dark fruit picks up the umami notes. An excellent opening pour — weight and fruit both land. Excellent; servers pour without second-guessing.",
