  "Austin Hope Cabernet Sauvignon|Brussels and Belly": "Brussels and Belly: the Brussels and Belly's smoky, sweet pork richness over bitter-char sprouts meets this structured red's cassis-and-dark-fruit frame, firm tannin, and oak-driven weight. The bold red's dark-fruit weight locks into the side's fat and umami; tannin cleans the dairy. A headliner pair — pour confidently. Excellent; servers pour without second-guessing.",
