  "Austin Hope Cabernet Sauvignon|Cowboy Ribeye": "Austin Hope — Paso Robles Cab with ripe plum, dark cherry, mocha, warm spice, plush full finish. Paso produces bigger warmer reds than Napa. The plush body handles Cowboy's marbled bone-in richness and the warm spice meets rendered fat. Peak Paso Cab for Cowboy — maximum richness for the big ribeye. Excellent; the pairing carries cleanly.",
